SYNOPSIS
========
Generate a to-do list containing new, modified, and current to-do items.  This can be used to generate a daily email, or viewed on a web page.  
On the web page, allow comments to be added, priorities and time estimates to be assigned, and tasks to be sorted by client, task, priority, and due date.

PROJECT OUTLINE (PHP / JS)
===============
PHP     1. Retrieve the list of tasks from the ProjectManagerSQL DB
PHP     2. Allow URL to send email vs. view in browser
PHP/JS  3. Web page:
JS          a. Allow sorting and filtering by:
                - client
                - task
                - due date
                    o Calendar input?
JS (H5?)    e. Calendar view
JS (H5?)    f. Allow tagging (how?)
            g. Fun: tag cloud

